ają na wyjeździe z belgijskim Knack Roselare. Rzeszowianie są w komfortowej sytuacji.","2026-03-11 20:04:33","Zrobić swoje. Asseco Resovia zagra rewanż z Roselare","zrobic-swoje-asseco-resovia-zagra-rewanz-z-roselare",{"comments":24},{"aid":929,"attachments":930,"category":943,"category_id":32,"featured":24,"id":944,"is_redirect":24,"lead":945,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":63,"published":63,"published_at":946,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":947,"slug":948,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":947,"uid":944,"updated_at":949,"stats":950,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},32291,{"id":931,"name":59,"url":932,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":933,"tags":59,"author":934,"type":851,"filename":935,"description":936,"750x750px":937,"160x90px":938,"365x225px":939,"100x100px":940,"760xautopx":941,"1200x675px":942},58409,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/9f94e8f7-8c1b-4565-aa9b-a921be208e45","2026-03-11 19:18:48","KS Developres Rzeszów","9f94e8f7-8c1b-4565-aa9b-a921be208e45","Siatkarki z Rzeszowa poległy w Turcji.","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/77e58cf6-c98e-456e-8923-84401db92af6","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/f118a950-a012-425e-b1c3-dd28f48b4b62","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/061e7966-a07c-4291-b2d6-55237bf43b24","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/a6a0411d-7d36-492b-89a1-c8d221c10c17","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/3a847402-1d60-47d1-a301-34ec709cc486","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/0880e5b1-a1e8-4e72-b744-7883662439e6",[103],"TzSy87FZOr3hCYOhwBuv","KS DevelopRes Rzeszów uległ Eczacibasi Dynavit Stambuł 1:3 w pierwszym starciu ćwierćfinałowym Ligi Mistrzyń. Mimo że polski zespół wygrał pierwszego seta, w kolejnych partiach dominowały już przeciwniczki.","2026-03-11 19:19:11","Rzeszowianki poległy w Stambule","rzeszowianki-polegly-w-stambule","2026-03-11 20:05:12",{"comments":24},{"aid":952,"attachments":953,"category":965,"category_id":62,"featured":24,"id":966,"is_redirect":24,"lead":967,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":63,"published":63,"published_at":968,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":969,"slug":970,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":969,"uid":966,"updated_at":971,"stats":972,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},32288,{"id":954,"name":59,"url":955,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":956,"tags":59,"author":850,"type":851,"filename":957,"description":958,"750x750px":959,"160x90px":960,"365x225px":961,"100x100px":962,"760xautopx":963,"1200x675px":964},58406,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/db3e4965-994d-4037-8924-2f9fbe67479e","2026-03-11 14:38:46","db3e4965-994d-4037-8924-2f9fbe67479e","Wypadek na Podkarpackiej w Rzeszowie","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/709caa1a-d7a5-425c-b5ec-3a66f353a003","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/e751385b-42af-495f-8814-af6b83c37d0a","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/bb6f2dd9-70bf-41ae-bc23-ad193dd6d2c3","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/bec9bb96-eac6-46b5-bb6a-ad586b984429","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/f7c2f7cf-1114-4757-8abe-d07f4a75ad07","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/1ab17ca5-e871-4805-90bf-afb988eaa4b5",[88],"An0qvXP40ACYeH6wFUnX","Poważne utrudnienia na wylotówce z Rzeszowa! Tuż po godzinie 13:00 na skrzyżowaniu ulic Podkarpackiej i Wetlińskiej doszło do groźnego zderzenia busa z pojazdem osobowym. Kierowcy muszą liczyć się ze sporymi korkami w tym rejonie – na miejscu pracują już służby, które starają się jak najszybciej udrożnić przejazd.","2026-03-11 14:41:12","Wypadek na Podkarpackiej w Rzeszowie. Spore utrudnienia w ruchu","wypadek-na-podkarpackiej-w-rzeszowie-spore-utrudnienia-w-ruchu","2026-03-11 15:34:10",{"comments":24},{"aid":974,"attachments":975,"category":988,"category_id":62,"featured":24,"id":989,"is_redirect":24,"lead":990,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":63,"published":63,"published_at":991,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":992,"slug":993,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":992,"uid":989,"updated_at":994,"stats":995,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},32285,{"id":976,"name":59,"url":977,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":978,"tags":59,"author":979,"type":851,"filename":980,"description":981,"750x750px":982,"160x90px":983,"365x225px":984,"100x100px":985,"760xautopx":986,"1200x675px":987},58403,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/4b33be30-7d6e-460f-8c73-1b9fbf719c7a","2026-03-11 13:38:05","Straż Miejska w Rzeszowie","4b33be30-7d6e-460f-8c73-1b9fbf719c7a","Wiosenne porządki na ulicach Rzeszowa","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/1b17f413-5a56-4c3e-a5aa-de49792ed9c3","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/efaf3b44-f197-438a-ad61-084c1a76f30f","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/e4b1dd9c-bbca-43cf-b21c-b4ad923bc005","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/c91d65e9-7021-4ea8-9778-166023361843","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/634ef758-5548-4a6b-a43b-72f7240e6013","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/528f4170-de52-44d9-b108-6168148cd85d",[88],"ERmwfi8gC8oPhvPZwXte","Koniec z osiedlowymi „pomnikami” na czterech kółkach! Rzeszowska Straż Miejska ruszyła z wiosennymi porządkami, usuwając z ulic zapomniane wraki, które od lat jedynie blokowały cenne miejsca parkingowe. Sprawdź, z których lokalizacji zniknęły już pierwsze „nieruchomości” i jak Ty możesz zgłosić auto, które ostatni raz wyjechało na trasę w ubiegłej dekadzie.","2026-03-11 13:38:38","Z rzeszowskich osiedli znikają samochody \"widmo\" [ZDJĘCIA]","z-rzeszowskich-osiedli-znikaja-samochody-widmo-zdjecia","2026-03-11 13:56:39",{"comments":24},{"name":997,"config":998,"type":1001},"Przycisk z linkiem",{"url":999,"text":1000},"https://rzeszow24.info/najnowsze","Więcej wiadomości","Button",{"module":1003,"size":32},[1004],{"name":35,"config":1005,"type":39},{"slot_id":42,"slot_view":292},{"color":49,"background":1007},"#F3F3F3",{"id":65,"config":1009,"variant":1011,"column":1012},{"background":1010,"color":49},"#ffffff",[826],[1013],{"size":826,"module":1014},[1015],{"name":35,"config":1016,"type":39},{"slot_id":462,"slot_view":38},{"variant":1018,"column":1019,"config":1207,"id":32},[32,32,32,32],[1020,1073,1127,1179],{"size":32,"module":1021},[1022,1049],{"type":842,"config":1023,"name":838,"articles":1025},{"type":1024,"query":21,"mobile_full":21,"mobile":14,"skip":126,"category":841,"limit":63,"mobile_intern":56},"ImageTile",[1026],{"aid":1027,"attachments":1028,"category":1041,"category_id":62,"featured":24,"id":1042,"is_redirect":24,"lead":1043,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":63,"published":63,"published_at":1044,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":1045,"slug":1046,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":1045,"uid":1042,"updated_at":1047,"stats":1048,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},32282,{"id":1029,"name":59,"url":1030,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":1031,"tags":59,"author":1032,"type":851,"filename":1033,"description":1034,"750x750px":1035,"160x90px":1036,"365x225px":1037,"100x100px":1038,"760xautopx":1039,"1200x675px":1040},58400,"https://storage.googleapi