a","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/8685868a-0481-4d8f-aaec-75aed2205bff","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/ba29820a-b7c2-4bc5-9696-44494a2519a6","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/1a1592ce-6c14-42b8-883b-69d035b4ba0c","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/cae18136-b106-47ec-aeb9-06874e9d499f",[88],"Zjkoc3aTF5de0DwZfHRH","W nocy z 14 na 15 lutego doszło do groźnego wypadku na jednej z głównych ulic Rzeszowa. Ustalane są przyczyny i przebieg zdarzenia.","2026-02-15 00:17:35","Poważny wypadek z udziałem radiowozu","powazny-wypadek-z-udzialem-radiowozu-maska-pojazdu-niemal-calkowicie-wgnieciona","Poważny wypadek z udziałem radiowozu. Maska pojazdu niemal całkowicie wgnieciona","2026-02-16 14:05:17",{"comments":24},{"size":32,"module":1506},[1507],{"name":1320,"config":1508,"type":1322,"articles":1509},{"mobile":56,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"content_type":56,"query":549,"limit":32,"skip":32,"selectedTag":1422},[1510,1531,1552],{"aid":1511,"attachments":1512,"category":1524,"category_id":62,"featured":24,"id":1525,"is_redirect":24,"lead":1526,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":1527,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":1528,"slug":1529,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":1528,"uid":1525,"updated_at":1503,"stats":1530,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},31193,{"id":1513,"name":59,"url":1514,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":1515,"tags":59,"author":1459,"type":851,"filename":1516,"description":1517,"750x750px":1518,"160x90px":1519,"365x225px":1520,"100x100px":1521,"760xautopx":1522,"1200x675px":1523},57215,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/edbfa329-707c-4dba-b94c-2706b4f6e819","2026-02-06 08:59:56","edbfa329-707c-4dba-b94c-2706b4f6e819","Wypadek na ulicy Przy Torze","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/e2aea459-4a64-4a26-91b0-573e69126282","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/26c177e2-5b38-41b5-8a63-d371023a5dae","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/c046fe34-1e90-4852-b6e4-71c3b902c1c8","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/9c6cafd6-217c-4f6b-a04c-9a438134c7c4","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/5779000f-6cac-4be1-838d-54ae3e96e8b2","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/b9cc4e8f-73dd-4d6a-ae6b-943156217c95",[88],"Wdfey2zjGVuFH8Fr0q8g","Poranny wypadek przy zbiegu ulicy Miłocińskiej i Przy Torze. Dziś, 6 lutego, przed godziną 8:00 doszło tam do zderzenia dwóch samochodów osobowych. Kierowcy muszą liczyć się z dużymi utrudnieniami – w miejscu zdarzenia ruch został znacznie spowolniony.","2026-02-06 09:02:13","Ślisko na drogach w Rzeszowie: wypadek przy ulicy Miłocińskiej [ZDJĘCIA]","slisko-na-drogach-w-rzeszowie-wypadek-przy-ulicy-milocinskiej-zdjecia",{"comments":24},{"aid":1532,"attachments":1533,"category":1544,"category_id":62,"featured":24,"id":1545,"is_redirect":24,"lead":1546,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":1547,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":1548,"slug":1549,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":1548,"uid":1545,"updated_at":1550,"stats":1551,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},31124,{"id":1534,"name":59,"url":1535,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":1536,"tags":59,"author":850,"type":851,"filename":1537,"description":853,"750x750px":1538,"160x90px":1539,"365x225px":1540,"100x100px":1541,"760xautopx":1542,"1200x675px":1543},57143,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/3a45babb-1a03-4e91-88ca-eb5d0c3dd453","2026-02-04 17:01:11","3a45babb-1a03-4e91-88ca-eb5d0c3dd453","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/5dd5bf18-9547-4d5c-ba1e-23a592c59905","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/ca948f42-164c-45c8-9c89-b84429cad421","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/1a4a2a96-7e8d-4614-bb12-7f98196dcf6a","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/0cf8a2cf-1959-454a-86b5-b894d3bbc7d6","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/c0b130d8-f6b9-4b51-b763-eb9ab4c23d77","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/9fe74de1-3ac7-4196-9520-0b381da2cfc9",[88],"a9aR1LTRFWVfuUTNOlBa","W środę, 4 lutego, tuż przed godziną 17:00 na drodze krajowej nr 19 w miejscowości Baryczka (powiat strzyżowski) doszło do groźnego zdarzenia drogowego. Na miejscu pracują służby ratunkowe, a kierowcy podróżujący tą trasą muszą liczyć się ze sporymi utrudnieniami w ruchu.","2026-02-04 17:04:13","Wypadek na DK19. Droga jest całkowicie zablokowana","wypadek-na-dk19-droga-jest-calkowicie-zablokowana","2026-02-05 11:54:19",{"comments":24},{"aid":1553,"attachments":1554,"category":1566,"category_id":62,"featured":24,"id":1567,"is_redirect":24,"lead":1568,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":1569,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":1570,"slug":1571,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":1570,"uid":1567,"updated_at":1550,"stats":1572,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},31049,{"id":1555,"name":59,"url":1556,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":1557,"tags":59,"author":850,"type":851,"filename":1558,"description":1559,"750x750px":1560,"160x90px":1561,"365x225px":1562,"100x100px":1563,"760xautopx":1564,"1200x675px":1565},57050,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/cab9dc14-ae83-4488-b081-82f38037322c","2026-02-02 16:44:24","cab