-i-prosi-o-pomoc",{"comments":24},{"module":2095,"size":32},[2096],{"name":838,"config":2097,"type":842,"articles":2098},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2036,"limit":63,"skip":65,"category":2036},[2099],{"aid":2100,"attachments":2101,"category":2113,"category_id":167,"featured":24,"id":2114,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2115,"locked":24,"origin_domain":2087,"parent_domain":2087,"parent_id":2116,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2117,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":2118,"short_title":2119,"slug":2120,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":2119,"uid":2114,"updated_at":1393,"stats":2121,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":63,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},30149,{"id":2102,"name":59,"url":2103,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2104,"tags":59,"author":2105,"type":851,"filename":2106,"description":59,"750x750px":2107,"160x90px":2108,"365x225px":2109,"100x100px":2110,"760xautopx":2111,"1200x675px":2112},56102,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/126091dd-9ebe-4cd5-b752-1a49be7f219d","2026-01-08 09:50:05","Hotel Arłamów","126091dd-9ebe-4cd5-b752-1a49be7f219d","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/a7436877-fd5b-45f0-a433-171e37feb3a0","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/0a38de82-a5e6-4ddb-aa11-74d084a6c2cb","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/95698dc7-2eb5-4439-9b12-8c19e281287c","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/3af42170-a4e7-4d11-9f9a-626faba088b6","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/b2c3d047-b1b3-4916-be15-370a4d07b8f3","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/f7859408-0df1-443f-88d7-dc98a0bf9c8f",[162],"p4AhTQZ6QNTV2jxRmgST","Hotel Arłamów z radością informuje, że w sobotę tj. 10 stycznia, uruchamiamy wyciąg numer 2 na Stacji Narciarskiej Arłamów! Jest to wyciąg orczykowy o długości 500 m, dzięki czemu od tej pory wszystkie trasy zjazdowe będą dostępne dla miłośników narciarstwa. Posiadamy 3 w pełni oświetlone trasy, co umożliwia jazdę nawet po zmroku, w tym bezpieczny wyciąg taśmowy dla dzieci.","FaLCEX8Glsg5il8Iixb8","2026-01-08 09:50:49","https://korsosanockie.pl/podkarpacie/sezon-w-arlamowie-nabiera-tempa-juz-w-sobote-otwarcie-kolejnego-wyciagu/FaLCEX8Glsg5il8Iixb8","Sezon w Arłamowie nabiera tempa! Już w sobotę otwarcie kolejnego wyciągu!","sezon-w-arlamowie-nabiera-tempa-juz-w-sobote-otwarcie-kolejnego-wyciagu",{"comments":24},{"module":2123,"size":32},[2124],{"name":838,"config":2125,"type":842,"articles":2126},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2036,"limit":63,"skip":32,"category":2036},[2127],{"aid":2128,"attachments":2129,"category":2141,"category_id":167,"featured":24,"id":2142,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2143,"locked":24,"origin_domain":2087,"parent_domain":2087,"parent_id":2144,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2145,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":2146,"short_title":2147,"slug":2148,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":2147,"uid":2142,"updated_at":1956,"stats":2149,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},29513,{"id":2130,"name":59,"url":2131,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2132,"tags":59,"author":2133,"type":851,"filename":2134,"description":59,"750x750px":2135,"160x90px":2136,"365x225px":2137,"100x100px":2138,"760xautopx":2139,"1200x675px":2140},55400,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/1f6010b4-697c-4e00-a6c3-88836b8a3baa","2025-12-19 10:16:51","Krosno112.pl","1f6010b4-697c-4e00-a6c3-88836b8a3baa","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/4157f2ad-44cc-4a69-94eb-48d760a210e3","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/9934b9c2-6c08-41b2-840f-23c03c7b2aa6","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/ca02baf2-c1db-4b09-a010-be70d8ef30f9","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/2fa425dc-aa80-4c11-b1a9-c2479e6a890f","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/c6eead82-7cd5-4e8a-bfe1-182fdebef8a2","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/2a3b9c00-0fa7-4a4b-9ade-f507f2dfc62e",[162],"t51DjxD9QjS0WCMITkRe","Dziś rano, 19 grudnia doszło do poważnego wypadku na głównym skrzyżowaniu w Łężanach, w gminie Miejsce Piastowe. Zderzenie dwóch samochodów skutkuje zablokowaniem skrzyżowania i dużymi utrudnieniami w ruchu. Dwie osoby wymagały pomocy medyków.","XkL6qbG2EJm4H1Xg3XAl","2025-12-19 10:18:18","https://korsosanockie.pl/podkarpacie/wypadek-na-skrzyzowaniu-w-lezanach-dwie-osoby-ranne/XkL6qbG2EJm4H1Xg3XAl","Wypadek na skrzyżowaniu w Łężanach. Dwie osoby ranne","wypadek-na-skrzyzowaniu-w-lezanach-dwie-osoby-ranne",{"comments":24},{"background":1010,"color":2151},"#444444",{"config":2153,"id":2155,"column":2156,"variant":2162},{"color":2154,"background":1670},"#100F0F",21,[2157],{"size":826,"module":2158},[2159],{"name":1222,"config":2160,"type":1225},{"title":2161,"link":194,"alternativeView":21},"POLSKA I ŚWIAT",[826],{"config":2164,"column":2165,"id":156,"variant":2285},{"background":1010,"color":2151},[2166,2196,2226,2255],{"size":32,"module":2167},[2168],{"name":838,"config":2169,"type":842,"articles":2171},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2170,"limit":63,"skip":24,"category":2170},"category:array-contains:polska-i-swiat",[2172],{"aid":2173,"attachments":2174,"category":2185,"category_id":192,"featured":24,"id":2186,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2187,"locked":24,"origin_domain":2188,"parent_domain":2188,"parent_id":2189,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2190,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":2191,"short_title":2192,"slug":2193,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":2192,"uid":2186,"updated_at":2194,"stats":2195,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":63,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},27017,{"id":2175,"name":59,"url":2176,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2177,"tags":59,"author":59,"type":851,"filename":2178,"description":59,"750x750px":2179,"160x90px":2180,"365x225px":2181,"100x100px":2182,"760xautopx":2183,"1200x675px":2184},52775,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso/articles/image/1fceae68-499a-42d6-9f4e-5243a8ad4e3a","2025-10-07 09:41:30","1fceae68-499a-42d6-9f4e-5243a8ad4e3a","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso/articles/image/26eaa419-b77c-413f-ad12-48648771aafd","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso/articles/image/a66c9056-63bb-4b08-aad7-9befe42666f4","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso/articles/image/31c3f4bb-3633-40df-9c0c-c81d131fc502","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso/articles/image/ff57d6a1-792c-4fb8-a3d7-bc7ca3da7029","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso/articles/image/93cb8cae-5b29-4ae4-bcde-44ca0afa340e","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso/articles/image/1a2e8458-42cf-44f9-851c-8d36741d3ef3",[189],"Cv7Eq12LNuWL2uKkqwUW","Wyobrażasz sobie nieoczekiwany koszt w wysokości 500 tysięcy złotych, który musisz ponieść, jeśli chcesz dalej pracować? Z takimi kolosalnymi wydatkami mogą spotykać się właściciele gospodarstw rolnych, którzy nie ubezpieczają swoich maszyn. Na szczęście takich rolników jest coraz mniej. Rośnie bowiem świadomość, że zawarcie polisy w ramach AgroCasco to inwestycja, a nie wydatek.","korso.pl","Iwn6fqhgeX8wnHoNklrX","2025-10-07 09:43:41","https://korso.pl/polska-i-swiat/ciagnikiem-wjechal-w-slup-wysokiego-napiecia-kto-zaplaci-za-naprawe-400-tys-zl/Iwn6fqhgeX8wnHoNklrX","Ciągnikiem wjechał w słup wysokiego napięcia. Kto zapłaci za naprawę 400 tys. zł?","ciagnikiem-wjechal-w-slup-wysokiego-napiecia-kto-zaplaci-za-naprawe-400-tys-zl","2025-10-08 19:46:41",{"comments":24},{"module":2197,"size":32},[2198],{"name":838,"config":2199,"type":842,"articles":2200},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2170,"limit":63,"skip":63,"category":2170},[2201],{"aid":2202,"attachments":2203,"category":2216,"category_id":192,"featured":24,"id":2217,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2218,"locked":24,"origin_domain":2056,"parent_domain":2056,"parent_id":2219,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2220,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":2221,"short_title":2209,"slug":2222,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":2223,"uid":2217,"updated_at":2224,"stats":2225,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},26717,{"id":2204,"name":59,"url":2205,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2206,"tags":59,"author":2207,"type":851,"filename":2208,"description":2209,"750x750px":2210,"160x90px":2211,"365x225px":2212,"100x100px":2213,"760xautopx":2214,"1200x675px":2215},52457,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsokolbuszowskie/articles/image/46c2747d-9a23-4310-9df3-3dace0bd2ea6","2025-09-26 13:38:55","Canva.com","46c2747d-9a23-4310-9df3-3dace0bd2ea6","Koniec z trzymaniem psów na łańcuchach. Sejm przyjął nowelizację ustawy","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsokolbuszowskie/articles/image/60788d72-8928-44eb-9fca-265167915682","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsokolbuszowskie/articles/image/d671c2b1-28c3-4c42-aed9-2f4bef80a714","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsokolbuszowskie/articles/image/9d64a352-ec25-49a0-ac8d-389bb401a128","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsokolbuszowskie/articles/image/96029edd-8015-4554-90c8-e48ea5d00df9","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsokolbuszowskie/articles/image/66451f40-35b1-46c8-a9d7-701c928bd552","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsokolbuszowskie/articles/image/7efe300b-aa2a-4789-88cb-f8042c4217d4",[189],"TbWOaKjZEOTV79esuSyD","Trzymanie psów na stałej uwięzi, np. na łańcuchu, zostanie zakazane – zdecydowali w piątek posłowie, uchwalając nowelizację ustawy o ochronie zwierząt. Do tej pory przepisy pozwalały na uwiązanie zwierzęcia do 12 godzin na dobę. Nowe regulacje wejdą w życie po 12 miesiącach od ogłoszenia.","b2wS97DmogTeiFrgBgzK","2025-09-26 13:41:10","https://korsokolbuszowskie.pl/polska-i-swiat/koniec-z-trzymaniem-psow-na-lancuchach-sejm-przyjal-nowelizacje-ustawy-sa-tez-zmiany-w-sprawie-kojcow/b2wS97DmogTeiFrgBgzK","koniec-z-trzymaniem-psow-na-lancuchach-sejm-przyjal-nowelizacje-ustawy-sa-tez-zmiany-w-sprawie-kojcow","Koniec z trzymaniem psów na łańcuchach. Sejm przyjął nowelizację ustawy. Są też zmiany w sprawie kojców","2025-10-08 13:37:14",{"comments":24},{"module":2227,"size":32},[2228],{"name":838,"config":2229,"type":842,"articles":2230},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2170,"limit":63,"skip":65,"category":2170},[2231],{"aid":2232,"attachments":2233,"category":2246,"category_id":192,"featured":24,"id":2247,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2248,"locked":24,"origin_domain":2087,"parent_domain":2087,"parent_id":2249,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2250,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":2251,"short_title":2252,"slug":2253,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":2252,"uid":2247,"updated_at":2224,"stats":2254,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},26282,{"id":2234,"name":59,"url":2235,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2236,"tags":59,"author":2237,"type":851,"filename":2238,"description":2239,"750x750px":2240,"160x90px":2241,"365x225px":2242,"100x100px":2243,"760xautopx":2244,"1200x675px":2245},51998,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/97dd7bec-7f2f-41fd-8f0a-e6cba7d4b42d","2025-09-10 11:07:14","Flaga Paktu Północnoatlantyckiego (NATO) wikipedia","97dd7bec-7f2f-41fd-8f0a-e6cba7d4b42d","Dzięki temu możliwe będzie podjęcie działań prewencyjnych i wzmocnienie bezpieczeństwa państw członkowskich w obliczu potencjalnych zagrożeń.","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/7029f13c-e8b9-413e-860c-00f9cb5c5f96","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/a4a0c078-1f8b-449a-a6eb-3a6cd47913b2","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/ce9a85fc-1176-4866-810a-a0d760a1bd1c","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/86ed449c-c105-4bd4-9598-98e9eca98f96","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/8224a27f-cedb-4a80-a818-d078363a8253","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/88db3923-1893-4c7f-ad5f-0fc2a9bc6992",[189],"GIzLyG4Xvj3TKcEj93Sk","Prezydent Karol Nawrocki oraz premier Donald Tusk podjęli decyzję o uruchomieniu artykułu 4 Traktatu Północnoatlantyckiego. Jest to procedura przewidziana w sytuacjach, gdy którekolwiek z państw członkowskich NATO uzna, że jego integralność terytorialna, niezależność polityczna lub bezpieczeństwo mogą być zagrożone.","rOK7riM7g8AQ2P6WVDW1","2025-09-10 11:07:28","https://korsosanockie.pl/polska-i-swiat/prezydent-i-premier-zdecydowali-o-uruchomieniu-artykulu-4-nato/rOK7riM7g8AQ2P6WVDW1","Prezydent i premier zdecydowali o uruchomieniu artykułu 4 NATO","prezydent-i-premier-zdecydowali-o-uruchomieniu-artykulu-4-nato",{"comments":24},{"module":2256,"size":32},[2257],{"name":838,"config":2258,"type":842,"articles":2259},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2170,"limit":63,"skip":32,"category":2170},[2260],{"aid":2261,"attachments":2262,"category":2274,"category_id":192,"featured":24,"id":2275,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2276,"locked":24,"origin_domain":2087,"parent_domain":2087,"parent_id":2277,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2278,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":2279,"short_title":2280,"slug":2281,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":2282,"uid":2275,"updated_at":2283,"stats":2284,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},24353,{"id":2263,"name":59,"url":2264,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2265,"tags":59,"author":281,"type":851,"filename":2266,"description":2267,"750x750px":2268,"160x90px":2269,"365x225px":2270,"100x100px":2271,"760xautopx":2272,"1200x675px":2273},49973,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/57801e25-cc6a-40ba-af2b-0046c9f35b36","2025-06-27 12:13:28","57801e25-cc6a-40ba-af2b-0046c9f35b36","Tragedia w Starej Wsi – młode małżeństwo nie żyje, jedna osoba ranna","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/8cd3fa39-f250-4ede-9aff-b88722f9afbb","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/4ca536b4-05c1-4101-bb1f-1fc1bef12048","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/c923a098-b911-44d3-9e7d-58374b5d9791","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/2a12dd08-bf80-4420-b8db-bf465aad0574","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/1b8835ed-d166-413f-ade7-19b6e889456a","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korsosanockie/articles/image/d3f046f5-499a-4dea-b6cb-4fa43ce18e91",[189],"cyohO9W1lnmA6b9EIIcp","27 czerwca, około godziny 10:00, w miejscowości Stara Wieś, w gminie Limanowa, doszło do dramatycznej strzelaniny. Z informacji potwierdzonych przez limanowską policję wynika, że w wyniku zdarzenia postrzelone zostały trzy osoby. Niestety, dwie z nich zginęły na miejscu, a trzecia osoba została poważnie ranna i trafiła do szpitala.","ADNBgKOWDFfsBBfeVsJB","2025-06-27 12:14:50","https://korsosanockie.pl/polska-i-swiat/strzelanina-w-starej-wsi-dwie-osoby-nie-zyja-trzecia-w-ciezkim-stanie-policja-prowadzi-oblawe/ADNBgKOWDFfsBBfeVsJB","Strzelanina w Starej Wsi. Trwa obława!","strzelanina-w-starej-wsi-dwie-osoby-nie-zyja-trzecia-w-ciezkim-stanie-policja-prowadzi-oblawe","Strzelanina w Starej Wsi: Dwie osoby nie żyją, trzecia w ciężkim stanie. Policja prowadzi obławę","2025-06-28 14:58:41",{"comments":24},[32,32,32,32],{"id":192,"config":2287,"variant":2288,"column":2289},{"background":1670,"color":49},[826],[2290],{"size":826,"module":2291},[2292],{"name":1222,"config":2293,"type":1225},{"title":2294,"link":201,"alternativeView":21},"PROMOWANE",{"column":2296,"variant":2504,"config":2505,"id":2506},[2297,2351,2402,2454],{"size":32,"module":2298},[2299,2327],{"name":838,"config":2300,"type":842,"articles":2302},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2301,"limit":63,"skip":24,"category":2301},"category:array-contains:promowane",[2303],{"aid":2304,"attachments":2305,"category":2316,"category_id":128,"featured":24,"id":2317,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2318,"locked":24,"origin_domain":2319,"parent_domain":2319,"parent_id":2320,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2321,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":2322,"short_title":2323,"slug":2324,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":2323,"uid":2317,"updated_at":2325,"stats":2326,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":63,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},32090,{"id":2306,"name":59,"url":2307,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2308,"tags":59,"author":59,"type":851,"filename":2309,"description":59,"750x750px":2310,"160x90px":2311,"365x225px":2312,"100x100px":2313,"760xautopx":2314,"1200x675px":2315},58205,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/2d327c33-b2d3-4e1f-b575-0080e89206cf","2026-03-05 10:13:17","2d327c33-b2d3-4e1f-b575-0080e89206cf","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/3c5a7a6e-496b-401d-8807-41404d8452c0","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/3acc7122-5445-404d-bea1-2142460eec8a","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/9d6a39fa-c9d6-4266-986d-afd7705c6ad2","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/de39e403-c176-4beb-acd8-3e5c43f3fbf8","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/3038b19e-7f1e-46cc-a3c3-645bf638a96e","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/145832aa-ab2f-42a3-be29-0e4c7f228906",[197],"fhXByBtU5ZvNShTdc9oC","Arłamów On Tour przystanek Warszawa – klucz to pytanie:  Jak się czujesz w niedzielę o 19:00?\nArłamów On Tour rozgrzał stolicę, gromadząc ponad 100 liderek biznesu, managerów, HR-owców \ni przedsiębiorców.","korso24.pl","KAiqAnELhsOC3PmlHt97","2026-03-05 10:15:02","https://korso24.pl/promowane/arlamow-on-tour-przystanek-warszawa/KAiqAnELhsOC3PmlHt97","Arłamów On Tour przystanek Warszawa","arlamow-on-tour-przystanek-warszawa","2026-03-05 10:15:10",{"comments":24},{"name":838,"config":2328,"type":842,"articles":2329},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2301,"limit":63,"skip":63,"category":2301},[2330],{"aid":2331,"attachments":2332,"category":2343,"category_id":128,"featured":24,"id":2344,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2345,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2346,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":2347,"slug":2348,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":2349,"uid":2344,"updated_at":2346,"stats":2350,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":63,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},31304,{"id":2333,"name":59,"url":2334,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2335,"tags":59,"author":59,"type":851,"filename":2336,"description":59,"750x750px":2337,"160x90px":2338,"365x225px":2339,"100x100px":2340,"760xautopx":2341,"1200x675px":2342},57347,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/5884aaef-64ad-4233-9525-ab5ab04e7edd","2026-02-09 10:39:03","5884aaef-64ad-4233-9525-ab5ab04e7edd","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/62c5be35-beca-486b-a940-e92b8a59b7da","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/1f06e4f3-cb73-4139-8351-5e86e0ceef0b","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/10c0e4d0-9d22-4297-b8f1-c5f1d17a7ce6","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/553b6497-4bb2-4e35-98de-01ada06afd4a","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/b63a9719-d023-434f-b994-0a3f2d783c88","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/1e202820-6eb6-4e53-a5cf-bb6b35e8e722",[197],"blilXcXSyt9C31qVShgD","Decyzja o współpracy z projektantem wnętrz coraz częściej pojawia się na etapie planowania remontu lub urządzania nowego mieszkania. Wynika to z rosnącej świadomości inwestorów, że funkcjonalna i estetyczna przestrzeń wymaga nie tylko dobrego gustu, ale także wiedzy technicznej. Projektant wnętrz łączy kompetencje estetyczne z praktycznym podejściem do ergonomii, instalacji i budżetu. Warto rozważyć taką współpracę zwłaszcza wtedy, gdy mamy do czynienia z nietypowym układem pomieszczeń lub ograniczonym metrażem. Specjalista potrafi zoptymalizować przestrzeń w sposób trudny do osiągnięcia samodzielnie. Dodatkowo pomaga uniknąć kosztownych błędów projektowych, które często ujawniają się dopiero po zakończeniu prac. Zatrudnienie projektanta to także oszczędność czasu, ponieważ proces decyzyjny zostaje uporządkowany i oparty na konkretnych rozwiązaniach.","2026-02-09 10:39:42","Kiedy warto zatrudnić projektanta wnętrz?","kiedy-warto-zatrudnic-projektanta-wnetrz","Kiedy warto zatrudnić projektanta wnętrz",{"comments":24},{"module":2352,"size":32},[2353,2379],{"name":838,"config":2354,"type":842,"articles":2355},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2301,"limit":63,"skip":65,"category":2301},[2356],{"aid":2357,"attachments":2358,"category":2369,"category_id":128,"featured":24,"id":2370,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2371,"locked":24,"origin_domain":2319,"parent_domain":2319,"parent_id":2372,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2373,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":2374,"short_title":2375,"slug":2376,"sponsored":14,"sub_title":56,"title":2375,"uid":2370,"updated_at":2377,"stats":2378,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},29957,{"id":2359,"name":59,"url":2360,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2361,"tags":59,"author":59,"type":851,"filename":2362,"description":59,"750x750px":2363,"160x90px":2364,"365x225px":2365,"100x100px":2366,"760xautopx":2367,"1200x675px":2368},55886,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/f4ba0a78-c66b-4e44-994d-fceefe37f301","2026-01-02 10:52:18","f4ba0a78-c66b-4e44-994d-fceefe37f301","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/27fe9623-4aa1-4844-bfb1-79947f7ae04d","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/1a29cdd4-cabc-4bb9-a04c-275342534b81","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/20f816b1-c39a-4f4c-9606-bf327fd38e5b","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/4bcfc18e-c657-4727-9109-fce263e2c176","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/cc782d7e-395f-481f-b587-3c4a79f0331b","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/korso24/articles/image/fc7197d4-b8bb-47d0-b15a-01e17f6b1d40",[197],"r03K8nNuqfFw8WanAqOt","Tego nikt się nie spodziewał. Gdy cała Polska szykowała się na spokojną noc sylwestrową, Hotel Arłamów zamienił się w sportowo-towarzyskie epicentrum kraju. Na jednym parkiecie spotkali się Marek Papszun, Maciej Sawicki, Bartek Ignacik, a całość rozkręcali Rafał Maserak i Aleksandra Szutenberg. Efekt? Noc Sylwestrowa, o której mówi się długo po ostatnim tańcu.","xB7yVCpF2Gk1yCsdCiDY","2026-01-02 12:00:00","https://korso24.pl/promowane/papszun-sawicki-i-maserak-na-jednym-parkiecie-tak-wygladal-najgoretszy-sylwester-w-polsce/xB7yVCpF2Gk1yCsdCiDY","PAPSZUN, SAWICKI i MASERAK na jednym parkiecie! Tak wyglądał NAJGORĘTSZY SYLWESTER w Polsce","papszun-sawicki-i-maserak-na-jednym-parkiecie-tak-wygladal-najgoretszy-sylwester-w-polsce","2026-01-02 13:20:26",{"comments":24},{"name":838,"config":2380,"type":842,"articles":2381},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2301,"limit":63,"skip":32,"category":2301},[2382],{"aid":2383,"attachments":2384,"category":2395,"category_id":128,"featured":24,"id":2396,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2397,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2398,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":2399,"slug":2400,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":2399,"uid":2396,"updated_at":2398,"stats":2401,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":63,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},29267,{"id":2385,"name":59,"url":2386,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2387,"tags":59,"author":59,"type":851,"filename":2388,"description":59,"750x750px":2389,"160x90px":2390,"365x225px":2391,"100x100px":2392,"760xautopx":2393,"1200x675px":2394},55142,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/d29e4b8a-2ef8-4a74-a845-f01962a9680f","2025-12-12 15:31:04","d29e4b8a-2ef8-4a74-a845-f01962a9680f","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/030f0668-59c0-430e-b2d6-e747ebc3ae8d","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/3487e0c1-eac9-4b99-a338-9c9dc35fe97c","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/32e29940-3b8a-4d16-930c-bd895e57790e","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/cc2b7ed9-a447-43f9-adca-7850510280c0","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/b533bbd8-68c7-48c5-8b86-1d0ddc53ab28","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/acbc9669-0ec9-4cc7-9f34-efdda1c4dabc",[197],"8jTgZMd7bY1dJf9K3qVg","Arłamów On Tour ruszył w Polskę – i zrobił to z rozmachem. 25 listopada w katowickiej Fabryce Porcelany odbyła się pierwsza odsłona projektu, który porusza wątek przewagi konkurencyjnej jakim jest zarządzanie dobrostanem i Arłamów wychodzi do świata biznesu. Formuła jest prosta: spotkać się bliżej ludzi, którzy realnie budują zespoły, kulturę organizacyjną i decydują o kierunkach zmian w firmach.","2025-12-12 15:31:14","ARŁAMÓW ON TOUR wystartował! Katowice jako pierwszy przystanek biznesowej trasy","arlamow-on-tour-wystartowal-katowice-jako-pierwszy-przystanek-biznesowej-trasy",{"comments":24},{"module":2403,"size":32},[2404,2430],{"name":838,"config":2405,"type":842,"articles":2406},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2301,"limit":63,"skip":128,"category":2301},[2407],{"aid":2408,"attachments":2409,"category":2422,"category_id":128,"featured":24,"id":2423,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2424,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2425,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":2426,"slug":2427,"sponsored":14,"sub_title":2426,"title":2426,"uid":2423,"updated_at":2428,"stats":2429,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":63,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},29198,{"id":2410,"name":59,"url":2411,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2412,"tags":59,"author":2413,"type":851,"filename":2414,"description":2415,"750x750px":2416,"160x90px":2417,"365x225px":2418,"100x100px":2419,"760xautopx":2420,"1200x675px":2421},55079,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/c5ba9401-db4e-4477-9990-15ccc53c2add","2025-12-11 08:24:01","pexels.com","c5ba9401-db4e-4477-9990-15ccc53c2add","Zaburzenia mikrokrążenia twarzy – dlaczego skóra traci „wsparcie od środka\" i jak to wpływa na jej jędrność i koloryt?","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/446f6d68-8d32-4088-b7e6-26e66609be3e","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/b47a285c-2ca4-4bc2-ad94-883da987f08d","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/6866d385-efa6-4dd6-aa42-8b1a36b2b42a","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/1c42d2f1-07c0-4a67-9e12-9c269025a6be","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/af5a8332-6412-4b54-b38c-d9be22f169e9","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/2b413eec-5101-4532-b180-d6eac431e0d4",[197],"EU9HnMdvMCWy6dTHXoxj","Zaburzenia mikrokrążenia w obrębie twarzy to problem, który pojawia się stopniowo i często długo pozostaje niezauważony. Skóra wydaje się bardziej matowa, mniej elastyczna, szybciej reaguje na zmiany temperatury i gorzej radzi sobie z codziennymi obciążeniami. Brakuje jej tak zwanego „wsparcia od środka”, czyli zdolności do sprawnego odżywiania i regeneracji dzięki odpowiedniemu przepływowi krwi i limfy. To z kolei odbija się na wyglądzie, komforcie i ogólnym samopoczuciu.","2025-12-11 08:24:29","Zaburzenia mikrokrążenia twarzy – dlaczego skóra traci „wsparcie od środka” i jak to wpływa na jej jędrność i koloryt?","zaburzenia-mikrokrazenia-twarzy-dlaczego-skora-traci-wsparcie-od-srodka-i-jak-to-wplywa-na-jej-jedrnosc-i-koloryt","2025-12-11 08:27:30",{"comments":24},{"name":838,"config":2431,"type":842,"articles":2432},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2301,"limit":63,"skip":62,"category":2301},[2433],{"aid":2434,"attachments":2435,"category":2447,"category_id":128,"featured":24,"id":2448,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2449,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2450,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":2451,"slug":2452,"sponsored":14,"sub_title":56,"title":2451,"uid":2448,"updated_at":2017,"stats":2453,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":63,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},28679,{"id":2436,"name":59,"url":2437,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2438,"tags":59,"author":2413,"type":851,"filename":2439,"description":2440,"750x750px":2441,"160x90px":2442,"365x225px":2443,"100x100px":2444,"760xautopx":2445,"1200x675px":2446},54545,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/6face30b-cefd-4227-a20e-529e032dfb10","2025-11-27 09:45:50","6face30b-cefd-4227-a20e-529e032dfb10","All Inclusive dla aktywnych","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/e0f15b06-e7d3-4c39-a61a-4fc8e829022b","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/1240ea9d-2001-449f-9ae5-7be213f4d7d1","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/a671dff4-be4f-4f30-82de-2bc04f0a127a","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/65b19249-296f-4823-bcba-16a18db2f75f","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/9f5585df-5dbf-4a48-ac10-ac0b017a982e","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/eaedc365-795b-4269-917c-8d6e1b180af3",[197],"tzpeP0A1s9EYJmztfpbp","Wczasy all-inclusive, choć często kojarzą się ze słodkim lenistwem i leżeniem z drinkiem przy basenie, mogą mieć bardziej aktywną formę. Warto korzystać z dostępnych w hotelu atrakcji, ale też wybierać się poza kurort. Sprawdź, co możesz robić, korzystając z oferty tego typu wakacji.","2025-11-27 08:50:39","All Inclusive dla aktywnych – jak nie przesiedzieć urlopu przy basenie","all-inclusive-dla-aktywnych-jak-nie-przesiedziec-urlopu-przy-basenie",{"comments":24},{"module":2455,"size":32},[2456,2479],{"name":838,"config":2457,"type":842,"articles":2458},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2301,"limit":63,"skip":126,"category":2301},[2459],{"aid":2460,"attachments":2461,"category":2472,"category_id":128,"featured":24,"id":2473,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2474,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2475,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":2476,"slug":2477,"sponsored":21,"sub_title":56,"title":2476,"uid":2473,"updated_at":2475,"stats":2478,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":24,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},28646,{"id":2462,"name":59,"url":2463,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2464,"tags":59,"author":59,"type":851,"filename":2465,"description":59,"750x750px":2466,"160x90px":2467,"365x225px":2468,"100x100px":2469,"760xautopx":2470,"1200x675px":2471},54497,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/80f92600-0673-45ea-bd51-ac7acfbe1a45","2025-11-26 13:01:39","80f92600-0673-45ea-bd51-ac7acfbe1a45","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/292fb359-21b6-4391-a6d9-8c8712df081d","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/5f42b81f-f8dc-44f8-b095-c10976dc268a","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/fab0ac4c-585f-4c7c-a437-a0f32208fa40","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/85275db0-fdd6-47e0-8fd9-0044820106ce","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/74cf05f8-4b82-4925-b0ca-f3832af09df9","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/d19a558f-5710-4aed-9948-7e257c4e9ec0",[197],"xRpOyRcKnVL2nNMxys6q","Są tacy, którzy zamiast kolejnej książki czy perfum wolą poczuć przyspieszone bicie serca, mocny zastrzyk emocji i wspomnienie, które zostanie z nimi na długo. Ekstremalne prezenty to sposób na podarowanie czegoś więcej niż przedmiotu – to doświadczenie, które staje się historią do opowiadania.","2025-11-26 13:01:59","Ekstremalne prezenty dla osób lubiących adrenalinę. 5 propozycji","ekstremalne-prezenty-dla-osob-lubiacych-adrenaline-5-propozycji",{"comments":24},{"name":838,"config":2480,"type":842,"articles":2481},{"mobile":14,"mobile_full":56,"mobile_intern":56,"type":1024,"query":2301,"limit":63,"skip":169,"category":2301},[2482],{"aid":2483,"attachments":2484,"category":2496,"category_id":128,"featured":24,"id":2497,"is_redirect":24,"lead":2498,"locked":24,"origin_domain":11,"parent_domain":56,"parent_id":56,"premium":24,"priority":1389,"published":63,"published_at":2499,"recommended":24,"redirect_url":56,"short_title":2500,"slug":2501,"sponsored":14,"sub_title":56,"title":2502,"uid":2497,"updated_at":2017,"stats":2503,"is_photostory":24,"is_advertisement":63,"is_pool":24,"show_quiz_cover":21,"view_type":872},28616,{"id":2485,"name":59,"url":2486,"thumbnail":59,"created_at":2487,"tags":59,"author":2413,"type":851,"filename":2488,"description":2489,"750x750px":2490,"160x90px":2491,"365x225px":2492,"100x100px":2493,"760xautopx":2494,"1200x675px":2495},54467,"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/0a63eca9-f046-4d8b-ad08-f60d03f416ed","2025-11-25 14:21:44","0a63eca9-f046-4d8b-ad08-f60d03f416ed","Naucz dziecko planowania i dzielenia pracy na etapy","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/5ba0e42c-7d65-44fd-a95f-21b6a96201f3","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/23da891f-f913-4e26-8a76-5a01461b8232","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/5f9c30a2-0f7f-47e5-9a7c-499c40605419","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/f4685e88-f2bd-43cd-8514-fc66e4844263","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/08f616a8-f62e-4a30-8f53-96493484dd29","https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/186c7de9-57f3-4f37-a9f1-8e63661ee295",[197],"ikX1qsiT3qxBLvNhcf5m","Skuteczna nauka nie musi oznaczać długich godzin spędzonych nad książkami. Dzieci często potrzebują jedynie odpowiednich warunków i właściwego planu, aby uczyć się szybciej i z mniejszym stresem. Jako rodzic możesz zrobić naprawdę dużo, żeby ułatwić im codzienną naukę. Oto 6 sposobów, które realnie wspierają naukę dziecka.","2025-11-25 14:22:49","Jak pomóc dzieciom skuteczniej się uczyć? Poznaj 6 sposobó","jak-pomoc-dzieciom-skuteczniej-sie-uczyc-poznaj-6-sposobow","Jak pomóc dzieciom skuteczniej się uczyć? Poznaj 6 sposobów",{"comments":24},[32,32,32,32],{"color":49,"background":1010},24,{"id":72,"config":2508,"variant":2509,"column":2510},{"background":1208,"color":1208},[826],[2511],{"size":826,"module":2512},[2513],{"name":2514,"type":2515},"Linia odstępu","Divider",{"id":2517,"config":2518,"variant":2519,"column":2520},26,{"background":1010,"color":49},[128,178],[2521,2526],{"size":128,"module":2522},[2523],{"name":874,"config":2524,"type":877},{"code":2525},"\u003Cimg src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/bieszczady/rzeszow24/articles/image/cc8ac679-0636-4c60-970f-35cf99e6c193\" alt=\"Rzeszów herb\" width=\"200\" style=\"float:right;\" />",{"size":178,"module":2527},[2528],{"name":874,"config":2529,"type":877},{"code":2530},"\u003Cp>Zapraszamy do śledzenia \u003Cstrong>news&oacute;w z Rzeszowa\u003C/strong>. Każdego dnia piszemy o tym, co jest ważne dla społeczności lokalnej i miłośnik&oacute;w miasta. Nasz \u003Cstrong>portal informacyjny z Rzeszowa\u003C/strong> dostarcza wiedzy na temat bieżących aktualności. Jest miejscem dyskusji i dialogu. Interesują Cię \u003Cstrong>wiadomości z ostatniej chwili z Rzeszowa i okolic\u003C/strong>? Jesteś w dobrym miejscu! Dziennikarze tworzący nasz \u003Cstrong>portal rzeszowski\u003C/strong> to doświadczeni redaktorzy. Każdego dnia zagłębiają się w \u003Cstrong>wydarzenia w Rzeszowie\u003C/strong>, aby dostarczyć Ci skondensowanej wiedzy na tematy istotne dla mieszkańc&oacute;w. Czytuj nas i podziel się naszymi materiałami z rodziną i znajomymi. \u003C/p>\n\u003Ch5>Najczęściej wyszukiwane:\u003C/h5>\n\u003Cp style=\"font-weight:700;\">\u003Ca href=\"https://rzeszow24.info/tagi/atrakcje-rzeszow\">atrakcje rzeszów\u003C/a>, \u003Ca href=\"https://rzeszow24.info/tagi/awaria-pradu-rzeszow\">brak prądu\u003C/a>, \u003Ca href=\"https://rzeszow24.info/tagi/basen-rzeszow\">basen rzeszów\u003C/a>, \u003Ca href=\"https://rzeszow24.info/tagi/bulwary-nad-wislokiem-w-rzeszowie\">bulwary nad wisłokiem w rzeszowie\u003C/a>, \u003Ca href=\"https://rzeszow24.info/tagi/festiwal-rzeszow\">festiwal\u003C/a>, \u003Ca href=\"https://rzeszow24.info/tagi/galeria-rzeszow\">galeria rzeszów\u003C/a>, \u003Ca href=\"https://rzeszow24.info/tagi/glogow-malopolski\">głogów małopolski\u003C/a>, \u003Ca href=\"http